<module status="bronze">
    <h>sgrìobh</h>
    <p><g>sgrìobh</g>
        <en>write</en> is a <a href="?xx=verbs/simple_verbs">simple verb</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>sgrìobh</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>sgrìobhaidh</m> – future independent ie. <en>will write</en></li>
                <li><m>sgrìobh</m> – past independent ie. <en>wrote</en></li>
                <li><m>sgrìobhadh</m> – verbal noun ie. <en>writing</en></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
